svg.script: function addHover(node) {node.setAttribute("class", node.getAttribute("class") + " hover")}function removeHover(node) {var className = node.getAttribute("class").split(" ");className.splice(className.indexOf("hover"), 1);node.setAttribute("class", className.join(" "))}function a(node, links) {document.getElementById("module" + node).setAttribute("class","hover");for(var i = 0; i < links; i++) {var link = document.getElementById("module" + node + "link" + i); if(link) addHover(link);}}function c() {var elements = Array.prototype.slice.call(document.getElementsByClassName("hover"));for(var i = 0; i < elements.length; i++) removeHover(elements[i]);}
